\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {11}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {Anchoring is robust to two natural confounds (paired $n=6$ Phase~4 conversations).} \emph  {Top row --- prior-answer ablation:} anchoring persists when prior answer text is suppressed (\texttt  {[PRIOR ANSWER REDACTED]}); mean shift $-3.4$~pp (Wilcoxon $p=0.625$); per-turn agreement 83.6\% (153/183 turns). \emph  {Bottom row --- quantization robustness:} INT4 vs.\ INT8 re-run yields 100\% per-turn agreement (184/184) and mean shift $+0.7$~pp ($p=1.0$). Left panels show paired per-conversation shifts; right panels show scatter on the $y=x$ diagonal.}}{18}{figure.11}\protected@file@percent }
